      "content": "i get the blood test thing but it takes forever to get an appointment and im already feeling kinda run down. if i was just doing it for like 4-6 weeks to get my levels up, i wouldnt actually overdose or anything right? like is there any real reason i cant just start the 50k dose now and stop once i feel better?",
