      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont want to deal with all that medical stuff right now. if i just take it with some calcium supplements and maybe some k2 i can basically manage it myself, right? like, if i just stay on the 50,000 iu for a few weeks and then drop back down to a normal dose, it's basically just a quick boost. you're saying there's a real chance of kidney issues from just a month of that?",
